{"tid":1660782,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"國際戰線行動: #Shout4HK (平野鈴子用廣東話講香港人加油 香港人反抗 五大訴求缺一不可 光復香港時代革命)","createTime":"2019-10-17T16:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T09:57:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d9f14c14e286cac86554f1dc54e82fa37e8323dd","tid":1660782,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:56:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/helphk.info/videos/2386082828374665/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhelphk.info%2Fvideos%2F2386082828374665%2F&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=bdb03e52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/helphk.info/videos/2386082828374665/</a><br />\n<br />\nHelp Hong Kong<br />\n6 hours ago &middot;<br />\n<br />\nLet&rsquo;s #Shout4HK !<br />\n<br />\nSupport HongKongers to fight for freedom and against totalitarianism. The 5 demands from the people are:<br />\n<br />\n① Full withdrawal of Face Mask Ban under Emergency Regulation Ordinance<br />\n② Retraction of the &ldquo;Riot&rdquo; characterisation<br />\n③ Release of arrested protestors, especially the students and the wounded<br />\n④ Legal and independent investigation of the Hong Kong Police&rsquo;s Brutality<br />\n⑤ Full democracy and universal suffrage for Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n𝟱 𝗱𝗲𝗺𝗮𝗻𝗱𝘀, 𝗡𝗢𝗧 𝗢𝗡𝗘 𝗟𝗘𝗦𝗦<br />\n<br />\n#Shout4HK 【How?】<br />\n➊ Film your shout out<br />\n➋ Upload it to your social media account<br />\n➌ Tag 3 friends and spread the words<br />\n<br />\n#StandwithHongKong<br />\n#FreeHongKong<br />\n<br />\nFollow us:<br />\n<a href=\"http://helphk.info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhelphk.info&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=f62c42a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://helphk.info</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/helphk.info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fhelphk.info&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=d02a8743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.com/helphk.info</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://instagram.com/helphk.info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhelphk.info&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=43921721\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/helphk.info</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://twitter.com/helphkinfo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhelphkinfo&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=873ea487\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/helphkinfo</a><br />\n<br />\n#香港人加油 #HGYGY<br />\n#香港人反抗 #HGYFK<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可 #5DSKK1BH<br />\n#光復香港時代革命 #GFHGSDKM<br />\n<br />\n咁多位香港人,唔好多謝喇<br />\n同我Tag晒你識嘅日本人入嚟啦<br />\n要多D人#Shout4HK呀<br />\n要佢地拍片呀<br />\n<br />\n唔喺FB就去下面Tag<br />\n<br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/helphkinfo/status/1184779095458103296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhelphkinfo%2Fstatus%2F1184779095458103296&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=e48e9aa3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhelphkinfo%2Fstatus%2F1184779095458103296&h=5c345d59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/helphkinfo/status/1184779095458103296</a><br />\n<br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B3t2D_1FFMR/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB3t2D_1FFMR%2F&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=edf71acd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB3t2D_1FFMR%2F&h=4234f33a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B3t2D_1FFMR/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人一齊努力集氣!"},{"pid":"83081a9b2863ce6071d9b89ec52f032cc8417ea9","tid":1660782,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa